snippet.textDisplay:
ba-la-ghal ula-be kamalehi

ka-sha-fadojabe  jamalehi

hasonat jamiao khisalehi

sallualaihe waalehi

 

karu tere naam pe ja fida

na bas ek jan do jahan fida

do jahan se bhi nahi ji bhara

karu kya karodo jahan nahi

sallualaihe waalehi …………….

 

na to mera koy kamal hai

na hai dakhl is me gurur ka

muje rakhte hain wo nigaah mai

ye karam hai mere huzur ka

sallualaihe waalehi …………….

jise chaha dar pe bula liya

jise chaha apna bana liya

ye bare karam ke hain fesle

ye bare nasib ki baat hai

sallualaihe waalehi …………….

 

yahi aarzoo jo ho sukhrru

mile do jahan ki aabru

main kahu gulaam hu apka

wo kahe ke hamko qubool hai

sallualaihe waalehi
